# Local build artifacts. `shards build` inside the container needs to
# regenerate these against the container's libc/arch — leaving a stale
# `lib.o` or grammar `*.o` from a host build (e.g. macOS arm64) makes
# the in-container static link choke with
#   "file format not recognized" / "ld returned 1 exit status"
# because the build.sh staleness check sees a newer .o than source.
bin/
src/ext/tree_sitter/runtime/lib.o
src/ext/tree_sitter/grammars/**/*.o

# Test + dev caches (not needed at runtime, slow down the build context
# transfer, and `spec/functional_test/fixtures/` is large).
spec/
.crystal/
.shards/

# Source control and IDE state — never relevant inside the image.
.git/
.gitignore
.github/
.claude/
.vscode/
.idea/
.DS_Store

# Documentation and release artifacts — not needed at runtime.
docs/
*.md
LICENSE

# Worktrees from agent runs.
.claude/worktrees/

# Lockfiles for non-Crystal deps — Crystal uses shard.lock which IS
# needed inside the container; leave it tracked.
